             was indicted for <rs id="t18140525-83-off487" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18140525-83-off487" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18140525-83-off487" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18140525-83-cd488" type="crimeDate">26th of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18140525-83-off487 t18140525-83-cd488"></join>, two seals, value 30 s. and a gold ring, value 4 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18140525-83-victim804" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Jones
                        <interp inst="t18140525-83-victim804" type="surname" value="Jones"></interp>
